   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Minibus for Special Needs Orphans in Macedonia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This Giving Tuesday, join us in providing a minibus for The JOY Home Day Center for special needs orphans. This week, we began accepting children, giving them a place where they they can experience hope and healing through individualized care and therapy. However, we can only reliably transport 3 children at a time, and bringing children in wheelchairs adds more complications. All money donated will go directly to purchasing a used transit van, and every gift is appreciated.</narrative>
  </description>
